<% content_for :title do %>Track your favourite artists and never miss another release...<% end %>
<% content_for :description do %>Login with Facebook to find artists you like. Listen to & buy tracks, with an easy to use timeline. Free notifications when artists release new tracks.<% end %>
<div class="content content-pad-115-bottom">
<div id="content-home">
<div class="home-left left">
	<h2 class="signika-txt home-white-header font-35">Track your favourite artists and never miss another release...</h2><br/>
	<div class="font-14 home-txt-1">Keep up to date with your favourite artists, and discover a new and exciting way to find music online.</div><br/>
	<%= link_to(user_omniauth_authorize_path(:facebook), :id => "fb-txt") do %>
	<div class="left fb-button fb-o-pad lucida-font font-logout fb-home-login"><i class="icon-facebook"></i><span class="home-login-txt">Login with Facebook</span></div>
	<% end %>
</div>
<div class="home-right right">
<%= image_tag "/images/macbook.png", :alt => "Macbook", :id => "macbook" %>
</div>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div id="home-points">
<ul>
<li class="left"><h3 class="signika-txt font-25 home-titles">Find artists you like</h3><br/>
<div class="font-13">SNGTRKR intuitively recognises which artists you've liked on Facebook, and supplies you with recommendations to build up your TRK'd artists.</div>
<%= image_tag "/images/home1.png", :alt => 'Recommendations', :id => 'home1' %></li>
<li class="left"><h3 class="signika-txt font-25 home-titles">Discover new music</h3><br/>
<div class="font-13">Looking to expand your music library? SNGTRKR makes it fun and exciting to discover new music with track previews, recommendations and purchase links.</div>
<%= image_tag "/images/home2.png", :alt => 'Music', :id => 'home2' %></li>
<li class="left"><h3 class="signika-txt font-25 home-titles">Keep up to date</h3><br/>
<div class="font-13">Stay in the loop with your personalised timeline of artist releases, old and new. Alongside regular notifications straight to your inbox.</div>
<%= image_tag "/images/home3.png", :alt => 'Timeline', :id => 'home3' %></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function() {
  $('.fb-home-login').click(function(){
    $('.home-login-txt').html('Logging in...');
  });
});

</script>